Name: Community Alliance Food Pantry
Description:
Community Alliance Food Pantry is open to all residents of the Owen/Withee school district. It is open from 10 o'clock to 12 o'clock on the first Tuesday of the month and from 3 o'clock to 5:30 on the 3rd Tuesday of the month.
Patrons are allowed to come 1 time per month and are welcome to come by appointment as well.
